Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.46,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:40.98,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Speckled Band
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:44.81,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:46.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:52.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:53.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:03.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ellen, the lady of the house is\Ncoming back from America any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in panicking.\NWe are fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:08.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:15.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that you knew\Nher for so long a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:15.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a composite picture!\NI can buy her trust with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:24.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She has an eye-popping\Namount of fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, you are the\Nservant of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had a better role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:39.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed this old house\Nwhere I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Miss Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking\Ncare of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:52.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'd forgotten\Nthat I had this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even back then, you were\Nalready very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:03:00.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to toddle to me\Ncalling out, "Roylee, Roylee."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:04.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you haven't changed a bit,\Nyou still look young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sweet thing to say\Nto an old woman like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for that delicious meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:17.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:27.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired\Nafter your long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my childhood room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:38.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ellen, please keep\Nyour voice down at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:43.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me by visiting\Nmy lab this late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to ruin my plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes, I have a letter for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:10.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, you've been receiving\Ninvestigation requests...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,from as far away as America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:12.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Roylott?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that another request\Nfor an investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:35.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Roylott, I have\Na letter for Miss Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from her fiancé, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:42.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious of him, being able to\Nmarry a girl of such wealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,and such beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,An unnecessary inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Giddy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you displayed\Nyour prowess, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I took more time than\Nexpected on that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:27.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The road's getting more desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the car appears to be sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not appears to be,\Nit's completely depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't cheer up a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, it is raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hand me a screwdriver?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Can you repair it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really starting to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to push the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, stay on top of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, just a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:10.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up and grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be run\Nover by my own car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Holmes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you injured, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I was good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat, it's them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!\NPlease stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:16.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.\NOur car broke down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,a seriously bad day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of this place,\Nmonsters are going to pop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, someone lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:03.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they can't hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Our car broke down...\Nin this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:14.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,May we see your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:21.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that.\NInvite them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Holmes, just a traveller.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Our car broke down in this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay with us until\Nthe car gets repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:39.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mean to be brash.\NWell, I'm called Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a garage in the back.\NYou can put your car in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.92,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.18,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ellen sure is beautiful and we can\Nhardly complain about the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.35,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the old woman is\Nrather unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the housekeeper\Nof my cousin, Roylott.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Roylott's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay him no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He studies the ecology of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a little odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is odd.\NI'm not good with oddballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:29.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to do some errands.\NHe should be back shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's early, but please go on to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I should repair my car tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:56.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected, he came\Nback some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In a house this big...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,it's no surprise that one wouldn't\Nnotice someone coming in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:06.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ellen's fiancé will arrive\Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We must finish the work before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do about, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't seen me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And hide this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Holmes is finished\Nwith the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But those footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe Miss Ellen has come\Nby for some conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure something\Nwas in front of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No strangers allowed in this house!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:55.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the oddball!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:05.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This house is cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this house\Nfor your own sake!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:39.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone! Gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The stairs are gone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dangerous\Ntrap they've set here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be getting desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Roylott.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Roylott's lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of place is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:55.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I scared Watson away\Nwhen he came into the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't allow anyone to enter the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a house! It's full of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How long does it take\Nto repair a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:08.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I won't move\Nfrom here until Holmes gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this spotted rope?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NWhy are you so panicky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:29.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:40.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you're done with the car,\Nwe should get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:43.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, for an old man,\Nhe's quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mumbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of this creepy house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:00.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get out of\Nthis creepy house quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's late, but we'll say goodbye\Nto Miss Ellen before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to go\Nat this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever have any trouble\Nplease contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten anything\Nhave you, Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:34.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:43.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, they left without noticing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but would\Nyou remain here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the car again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain to you why later.\NI must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.\NStay awake tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's supposed to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:28.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were leaving, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?! Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You happen to be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Remain here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A venomous snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I hate snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:15.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes must have called for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, what's going on?!\NWhat happened to the crooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming,\NInspector Lestrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably in the back garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around to the back garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're using a balloon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch us if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making stupid faces\Nand pedal faster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your luck's run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you in my hands soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:21.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:23.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still going down!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep pedalling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle, tickle, tickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:45.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:55.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:56.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:11.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know\Nthat I was in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just arrived from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried when\Nyour letters didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been sending you\Na letter every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:30.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny, do you know Mr. Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he didn't receive your letters,\Nhe asked me to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:37.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cousin, Roylott,\Nwas destroying the letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:38.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:43.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Roylott died of an illness\N10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who was that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a villain named Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He was after the\Nvaluables in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:51.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He was planning to\Nsell the dinosaurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:56.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,that your cousin,\Nthe archaeologist, unearthed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,and sell to a museum\Nfor profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:01.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, why didn't you\Nexplain that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:07.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but it was the\Nonly way to fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:12.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone knew but me!\NI feel like a clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:14.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't catch the Roylott imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:19.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll live happily ever after.\NIsn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:24.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:27.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Snake!
