Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:45.54,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Producer\NHENRY GOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.58,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
