Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:24:00.35,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,While servicing the beloved\Nprototype Mercedes Benz...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:02.72,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes and I were abducted\Nand taken to the Naval Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:05.65,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,The case begins with the\Ndisappearance of a submarine...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:11.66,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,and involves an undersea treasure\Ndiscovered by adventurer, Raythunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:17.16,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If ever you find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
